---
// Features grid for Orbit AI marketing site
---

<section id="features" class="section max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <div class="badge mb-3">BUILT FOR DEVELOPERS WHO VALUE FOCUS</div>
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tighter">Everything you need.<br />Nothing you don't.</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-zinc-400 max-w-md mx-auto">A focused tool that combines the best parts of VS Code with first-class AI — without the bloat.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
    <div class="card rounded-2xl p-6">
      <div class="feature-icon mb-5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z" /></svg></div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Contextual AI Chat</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-[15px]">Groq-powered assistant that understands your current file. Streamed responses. One-click <span class="font-medium text-zinc-300">"Insert at cursor"</span> or "Replace selection".</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card rounded-2xl p-6">
      <div class="feature-icon mb-5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 4l-4 4 4 4" /></svg></div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Monaco Editor</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-[15px]">The same editor engine that powers VS Code. Full IntelliSense, syntax highlighting, multi-cursor, and all the keyboard shortcuts you already know.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card rounded-2xl p-6">
      <div class="feature-icon mb-5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg></div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Integrated Terminal</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-[15px]">Real PowerShell via node-pty. No fake terminal. Run any command, see live output, works with the folder you have open.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card rounded-2xl p-6">
      <div class="feature-icon mb-5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 7v10a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2h-6l-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2z" /></svg></div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">True Local Filesystem</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-[15px]">Open any folder on your machine. Recursive file tree, instant read/write. Your code never leaves your computer.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card rounded-2xl p-6">
      <div class="feature-icon mb-5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg></div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Fast &amp; Lightweight</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-[15px]">Electron app that starts fast and stays responsive. No indexing the entire internet. No waiting for cloud sync.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card rounded-2xl p-6">
      <div class="feature-icon mb-5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 8.944 11.922a12.025 12.025 0 01-1.48-.093" /></svg></div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Privacy by Default</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-[15px]">You bring your own Groq API key. Keys live only in localStorage. No accounts. No telemetry. No project uploads.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
